          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1630422183057-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1630422183057-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until thickened to a gravy-like consistency</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>lentil mixture</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>lentil mixture</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>(save the pan for later!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1630422185960-x200.jpg",
